      <title>中国暂停10个月后再次上调海外投资限额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/china-raises-limit-on-overseas-investment-after-10-month-pause</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国自七月以来首次取消了对海外证券投资的限制，此举可能有助于满足部分日益增长的海外资产需求，尽管北京方面正寻求提振国内市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/china-raises-limit-on-overseas-investment-after-10-month-pause</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 05:05:46 GMT</pubDate>
